OL,3,C'It's an exciting time' - reaction as
OL,4,Cwhisky tariffs cut by Donald Trump
OL,6,FThere's been widespread optimism
OL,7,Facross Scotland as the 10% tariff on
OL,8,Fwhisky was lifted on June 24.
OL,10,FFirst Minister, John Swinney has said
OL,11,Fthere will be a "significant benefit"
OL,12,Ffor Scottish producers as US tariffs
OL,13,Fon imports of Scotch whisky and lifted.
OL,15,FWhen the the tariffs were introduced
OL,16,Fbetween May and October of 2025, sales
OL,17,Fdropped off.
OL,19,FHowever, Donald Trump's administration
OL,20,Fimposed a new 10% tariff on UK imports
OL,21,Ffor other goods
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@eO]
