OL,3,C'It's an exciting time' - reaction as
OL,4,Cwhisky tariffs cut by Donald Trump
OL,6,FThe Annandale Distillery is one of
OL,7,FScotland's oldest working
OL,8,Fdistilleries: "We're really excited
OL,9,Fthat this has finally come the return
OL,10,Fto zero for zero conversion with the
OL,11,FUS," Lee Medd said.
OL,13,F"The money we're saving on this really
OL,14,Fwill allow us to reinvest in not just
OL,15,Fhere at the distillery, but our
OL,16,Fbottling hall, and ultimately create
OL,17,Fmore products and more jobs here in
OL,18,Fthe region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
