PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784913523
OL,3,C'It's an exciting time' - reaction as
OL,4,Cwhisky tariffs cut by Donald Trump
OL,6,F"It means we can get our whisky over
OL,7,Fthere. It's at a fair cost for our US
OL,8,Faudience. And again, we can get
OL,9,Fbarrels from Kentucky and from the US
OL,10,Fover here to to produce our single
OL,11,Fcast single malt Scotch whisky."
OL,13,FThe US president announced in April
OL,14,Fthat he would remove the whisky
OL,15,Ftariff, following the state visit by
OL,16,Fthe King and Queen.
OL,18,FThe industry body also welcomed the
OL,19,Fremoval of tariffs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
