OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784913523
OL,3,C'It's an exciting time' - reaction as
OL,4,Cwhisky tariffs cut by Donald Trump
OL,6,FIan Duddy, international director at
OL,7,Fthe Scotch Whisky Association, said:
OL,8,F"The return of tariff-free trade for
OL,9,FScotch whisky in the US is welcome
OL,10,Fnews for businesses on both sides of
OL,11,Fthe Atlantic.
OL,13,F"As Scotch whisky's most valuable
OL,14,Fglobal market, worth #933 million in
OL,15,F2025, the removal of tariffs provides
OL,16,Fgreater confidence to invest, grow
OL,17,Fexports, and support jobs and
OL,18,Fcommunities across Scotland and the US.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
