OL,3,C'It's an exciting time' - reaction as
OL,4,Cwhisky tariffs cut by Donald Trump
OL,6,F"On behalf of the Scotch whisky
OL,7,Findustry, we are grateful to everyone
OL,8,Fwho worked to make this happen,
OL,9,Fincluding His Majesty The King during
OL,10,Fhis recent state visit."
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,13,Four political experts are across all
OL,14,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,15,Fto the latest episode below...
